:- table p/1,q/1. 
:- incr p/1.
:- incr q/1. % cannot be defined as :- incr p/1, q/1.

p(X):- q(X),not r(X).
q(X):- c(X).


:- table r/1.
:- incr r/1.


r(X):- a(X).
r(X):- r(Y),b(Y,X).


:- dynamic a/1, b/2, c/1.

:- incrdynamic a/1.
:- incrdynamic b/2.
:- incrdynamic c/1.

:- assert(a(1)).
:- assert(b(1,2)).
:- assert(c(3)).
